title: Put Up or Shut Up
subTitle: In this special and unequal battle, cars and motorbikes compete against each other. Tom Bailey competes with his Chevy Camaro with V8 engine whilst Jeremy Teasley competes with his 700 hp racing motorbike.

title: Put Up or Shut Up
subTitle: At the Blair Bedford Dirt Drags in Pennsylvania, two top fuel bikes compete against each other. The focus there is on acceleration with nitromethane. The distance is only 150 metres so every second counts.

title: Salvage Hunters: Classic Cars
subTitle: With iconic Peugeot 205 GTI's more in demand than ever and prices rocketing, Drew and Paul gamble on restoring an insurance right-off.

title: Garage Rehab
subTitle: Richard Rawlings invests in a struggling garage, Scotty's Automotive, in Texas. The owner must break his hoarding ways for Richard to make his money back.

title: Dirt Every Day
subTitle: When Fred and his crew hear that Yellowstone Off-Road Racing is holding a 200-mile race on a Montana ranch, they pick up a Toyota 4Runner in order to modify it, and get it race ready .

title: Dirt Every Day
subTitle: Fred and Dave head to a friend's ranch and discover their old van derelict. They are determined to transform the 1979 Ford van into a ranch truck that their friend will be proud to drive.
